# Restaurant Booking Plugin Modernization - Phase Breakdown

## 🎯 Project Overview
Modernize existing WordPress restaurant booking plugin theo Figma design: https://www.figma.com/community/file/1308435721888237413

**Strategy**: Chia thành 8 phases độc lập, mỗi phase có deliverable cụ thể và có thể test riêng biệt.

---

## 📋 Phase Structure

### **Phase 1: Foundation & Design System** ⭐ (Ưu tiên cao)
- **Duration**: 1-2 days
- **Deliverable**: CSS design system, variables, base components
- **Dependencies**: None
- **Test**: Style guide page

### **Phase 2: Customer Booking Modal** ⭐ (Ưu tiên cao)  
- **Duration**: 2-3 days
- **Deliverable**: Modern booking widget với 3 steps
- **Dependencies**: Phase 1
- **Test**: Booking flow end-to-end

### **Phase 3: Portal Login & Authentication** ⭐ (Ưu tiên cao)
- **Duration**: 1-2 days  
- **Deliverable**: Modern login interface
- **Dependencies**: Phase 1
- **Test**: Login/logout flow

### **Phase 4: Portal Dashboard** 
- **Duration**: 2-3 days
- **Deliverable**: Manager dashboard với stats
- **Dependencies**: Phase 1, 3
- **Test**: Dashboard metrics display

### **Phase 5: Booking Management Interface**
- **Duration**: 2-3 days
- **Deliverable**: Bookings table, calendar view
- **Dependencies**: Phase 1, 3
- **Test**: CRUD operations

### **Phase 6: Table & Customer Management**
- **Duration**: 2-3 days
- **Deliverable**: Table floor plan, customer profiles
- **Dependencies**: Phase 1, 3
- **Test**: Table operations, customer history

### **Phase 7: WordPress Admin Enhancement**
- **Duration**: 2-3 days
- **Deliverable**: Modern WP admin interface
- **Dependencies**: Phase 1
- **Test**: Admin functionality

### **Phase 8: Mobile Optimization & Polish**
- **Duration**: 1-2 days
- **Deliverable**: Mobile responsive, animations
- **Dependencies**: All previous phases
- **Test**: Mobile user experience

---

## 🔄 Implementation Order

### **Sprint 1** (Week 1)
- Phase 1: Foundation & Design System
- Phase 2: Customer Booking Modal
- Phase 3: Portal Login & Authentication

### **Sprint 2** (Week 2)  
- Phase 4: Portal Dashboard
- Phase 5: Booking Management Interface

### **Sprint 3** (Week 3)
- Phase 6: Table & Customer Management
- Phase 7: WordPress Admin Enhancement

### **Sprint 4** (Week 4)
- Phase 8: Mobile Optimization & Polish
- Testing & Bug fixes
- Documentation

---

## 📁 Files Structure by Phase

```
restaurant-booking-manager/
├── Phase 1 - Foundation/
│   ├── assets/css/design-system.css
│   ├── assets/css/components.css
│   └── assets/js/theme-manager.js
├── Phase 2 - Customer Booking/
│   ├── assets/css/booking-modal.css
│   ├── assets/js/booking-widget.js
│   └── public/partials/booking-modal.php
├── Phase 3 - Portal Auth/
│   ├── assets/css/portal-auth.css
│   ├── assets/js/portal-auth.js
│   └── public/partials/portal-login.php
├── Phase 4 - Dashboard/
│   ├── assets/css/portal-dashboard.css
│   ├── assets/js/dashboard.js
│   └── public/partials/portal-dashboard.php
├── Phase 5 - Booking Management/
│   ├── assets/css/booking-management.css
│   ├── assets/js/booking-management.js
│   └── public/partials/booking-table.php
├── Phase 6 - Tables & Customers/
│   ├── assets/css/table-management.css
│   ├── assets/js/table-management.js
│   └── public/partials/table-floor-plan.php
├── Phase 7 - WP Admin/
│   ├── admin/css/modern-admin.css
│   ├── admin/js/modern-admin.js
│   └── admin/partials/admin-dashboard.php
└── Phase 8 - Mobile & Polish/
    ├── assets/css/mobile-responsive.css
    ├── assets/css/animations.css
    └── assets/js/mobile-enhancements.js
```

---

## ✅ Success Criteria per Phase

### Phase 1
- [ ] CSS variables system working
- [ ] Base components rendered correctly
- [ ] Dark/light mode toggle functional

### Phase 2  
- [ ] Modal opens/closes smoothly
- [ ] 3-step navigation works
- [ ] AJAX booking submission successful
- [ ] Form validation working

### Phase 3
- [ ] Login form styled correctly
- [ ] Authentication flow works
- [ ] Session management intact

### Phase 4
- [ ] Dashboard loads with real data
- [ ] Stats cards display correctly
- [ ] Navigation sidebar functional

### Phase 5
- [ ] Bookings table shows data
- [ ] Filtering/sorting works
- [ ] CRUD operations functional

### Phase 6
- [ ] Table floor plan displays
- [ ] Customer profiles accessible
- [ ] Management actions work

### Phase 7
- [ ] WP admin styled consistently
- [ ] All admin functions work
- [ ] Settings panels functional

### Phase 8
- [ ] Mobile responsive on all screens
- [ ] Animations smooth and performant
- [ ] Touch interactions optimized
